freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: I have 2 symptoms Ive not had in past but may or may not be related.  The day I received the vaccine I was very cold especially hands and feet. This has been occurring once or twice a wk. Second I have R knee joint pain for the last week, no injur
Last evening a little SOB. Very achy today relieved w Motrin. Just didnt feel like getting out of bed.

freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: Felt very cold but no chills and felt like I had to lie down from 4pm  yesterday until I went to bed. Feel much better today.
